               <head>A exegetical treatise on the tantric path and practice</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>NOTE: This record has yet to be fully checked.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="MS_Tibet_b_24_10_R-item1">
                     <title key="work_841" xml:lang="bo">རྡོ་རྗེ་བདེ་སྐྱིད་ཆེན་མོ་བཞུགས་སོ</title>
                     <title key="work_841" xml:lang="bo-Latn-x-EWTS">rdo rje bde skyid chen mo bzhugs so</title>
                     <note>The text is a very articulate exegesis of tantric practices, closely related to bKa' rgyud pa tradition in its content. It is very scholarly and well laid out but it seems to be incomplete.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="bo">rdo rje chen po'i snyan brgyud gsang ba'i nye lam mthun mongs ma yin pa snyams su len pa'i rim pa ni/_lta bas thag gcad pa dang /_sgom pas nyams su blang ba dang /_snyams su blang ba'i 'bras bu dang gsum du bsdus/_dang po lta bas thag bcad pa ni/_chos thams cad blo la ltos nas don dam dang kun rdzob gnyis su 'jog/</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="bo">spyod pa 'jigs bral rdo rje'i mtshon cha la 'byor pa can gtsang sbra rnams gsum gyi sgo nas kun bzang gi skyod pa mthar phyung ba/_ku su li spyod yul bzhi'i sgo nas gsang spyod lam du slong ba/_nus ldan gyi gang zag rig pa'i brtul shugs la brten nas he ru ka'i rol pas 'da' ba/_sangs rgyas kha ma dngos grub kyi nyer rgyud phyogs las rnam rgyal gyi spyod pa rtsis kyi bzhi'o//</explicit>
                     <textLang mainLang="bo">Tibetan</textLang>
                  </msItem>
